{"parse":{"title":"ECL Language tests","pageid":46212568,"revid":829609466,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n\n</p>\n<table class=\"plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-content ambox-multiple_issues compact-ambox\" role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/40px-Ambox_important.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/60px-Ambox_important.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/80px-Ambox_important.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"40\" data-file-height=\"40\" /></div></td><td class=\"mbox-text\"><div class=\"mbox-text-span\"><div class=\"mw-collapsible\" style=\"width:95%; margin: 0.2em 0;\"><b>This article has multiple issues.</b> Please help <b><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=ECL_Language_tests&amp;action=edit\">improve it</a></b> or discuss these issues on the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Talk:ECL_Language_tests\" title=\"Talk:ECL Language tests\">talk page</a></b>. <small><i>(<a href=\"/wiki/Help:Maintenance_template_removal\" title=\"Help:Maintenance template removal\">Learn how and when to remove these template messages</a>)</i></small>\n<div class=\"mw-collapsible-content\" style=\"margin-top: 0.3em;\">\n      <table class=\"plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-content ambox-Notability\" role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/40px-Ambox_important.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/60px-Ambox_important.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/80px-Ambox_important.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"40\" data-file-height=\"40\" /></div></td><td class=\"mbox-text\"><div class=\"mbox-text-span\">The topic of this article <b>may not meet Wikipedia's <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Notability\" title=\"Wikipedia:Notability\">general notability guideline</a></b>.<span class=\"hide-when-compact\"> Please help to establish notability by citing <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Identifying_reliable_sources\" title=\"Wikipedia:Identifying reliable sources\">reliable secondary sources</a> that are <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Identifying_and_using_independent_sources\" title=\"Wikipedia:Identifying and using independent sources\">independent</a> of the topic and provide significant coverage of it beyond a mere trivial mention. If notability cannot be established, the article is likely to be <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Merging\" title=\"Wikipedia:Merging\">merged</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Redirect\" title=\"Wikipedia:Redirect\">redirected</a>, or <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Deletion_policy\" title=\"Wikipedia:Deletion policy\">deleted</a>.<br /><small><span class=\"plainlinks\"><i>Find sources:</i>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.google.com/search?as_eq=wikipedia&amp;q=%22ECL+Language+tests%22&amp;num=50\">\"ECL Language tests\"</a>&#160;\u2013&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.google.com/search?tbm=nws&amp;q=%22ECL+Language+tests%22+-wikipedia\">news</a>&#160;<b>\u00b7</b> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.google.com/search?&amp;q=%22ECL+Language+tests%22+site:news.google.com/newspapers&amp;source=newspapers\">newspapers</a>&#160;<b>\u00b7</b> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.google.com/search?tbs=bks:1&amp;q=%22ECL+Language+tests%22+-wikipedia\">books</a>&#160;<b>\u00b7</b> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//scholar.google.com/scholar?q=%22ECL+Language+tests%22\">scholar</a>&#160;<b>\u00b7</b> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.jstor.org